    "description": {
      "value": "<h4><span id=\"Mead_Wasp\"><a name=\"TOC-Mead-Wasp\"></a>Mead, Wasp</span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a href=\"https://amzn.to/2pCBzMR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PPC:MM</a></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 400 gp; <b>Weight</b> 2 lbs.</p>\r\n<p>A rare breed of wasp produces the honey used to make this spiced, mead-like drink. For 1 hour after consuming a glass of wasp mead (this takes 1 round), the drinker is quick to respond to harm, gaining a +1 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Bonus-Alchemical-\">alchemical bonus</a> on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Attack-Roll\">attack rolls</a> against any creature that has damaged her with an attack within the previous round. This bonus does not stack with itself. A typical <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/containers-bags-boxes-more#TOC-Bottle\">bottle</a> holds four glasses' worth of wasp mead.</p>\r\n",
